                    <span class="text-sm font-medium">ðŸš€ Now in v1.0</span>
                </div>

                <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
                    Command Your
                    <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                            Development
                        </span>
                    Workflow
                </h1>

                <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    Stop juggling 10+ terminal windows. Gomander is the simple GUI that lets you launch, monitor, and organize all your commands in one beautiful interface.
                </p>

                <!-- Primary CTA -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-8">
